  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency Assistance to Displaced Populations in Chad: Displacement Tracking Matrix</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IOM seeks to strengthen its humanitarian interventions and collaborationwith national emergency responders to address the needs of internally displaced persons (IDPs), returnees, third country nationals and host communities, keeping in mind the cross-border and regional implications of the crises affecting Chad, through the provision of displacement-related information to the humanitarian community, government and other stakeholders, the analysis of trafficking in peoplephenomenon, and the direct assistance to stranded migrants.</narrative>
  </description>
